<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Story | Homie Cafe</title>
    
</head>
<body>
    <!-- This skip link appears when keyboard users press Tab, allowing them to jump directly to the main page content instead of tabbing through every navigation item. -->
    <a class="skip-link" href="#mainContent">Skip to main content</a>

    <!-- This fixed header contains the brand name, responsive navigation links, search link, order link, and theme switcher required for the website theme toggle feature. -->
    <header class="site-header" id="siteHeader">
        <div class="nav-wrap">
            <a href="index.html" class="brand" aria-label="Homie Cafe homepage">Homie Cafe</a>

            <!-- This button appears on smaller screens and opens or closes the navigation menu using JavaScript in main.js. -->
            <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" type="button" aria-label="Open navigation menu" aria-expanded="false">
                ☰
            </button>

            <!-- This navigation menu links to all major website pages so the multi-page website can be accessed consistently from every page. -->
            <nav class="main-nav" id="mainNav" aria-label="Main navigation">
                <a href="index.html">Home</a>
                <a href="catalogue.html">Menu</a>
                <a href="about.html">Our Story</a>
                <a href="team.html">Team</a>
                <a href="reviews.html">Reviews</a>
                <a href="catalogue.html" aria-label="Search products">Search</a>
                <a href="register.html">Register</a>
                <a href="login.html" class="order-link">Login</a>

                <!-- This button changes the website between light theme and dark theme -->
                <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" type="button" aria-label="Switch website theme">
                    Theme
                </button>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>


    <main id="mainContent" class="page-main">
        <!-- This page hero introduces the brand story page and explains the purpose of the Alyriss Coffee concept. -->
        <section class="simple-hero">
            <p class="eyebrow dark">Our Story</p>
            <h1>More Than Just a Coffee</h1>
            <p>
                Alyriss Coffee is a fictional premium coffee shop created for the Web Fundamentals assignment.
                The brand focuses on carefully roasted beans, warm service, and a relaxing cafe atmosphere.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- This two-column story section explains the client background and design direction, which can later be reused in the group report. -->
        <section class="about-story section-padding" aria-labelledby="about-story-title">
            <div class="about-image">
                <!-- ABOUT IMAGE: Replace this online image with a local cafe interior image before final submission if required. -->
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501339847302-ac426a4a7cbb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Warm coffee shop interior">
            </div>

            <div class="about-text">
                <p class="eyebrow dark">Brand Background</p>
                <h2 id="about-story-title">A calm place for better coffee moments.</h2>
                <p>
                    The website is designed to help customers explore Alyriss Coffee's menu, learn about the brand,
                    submit reviews, and register as simulated members. The design uses dark coffee tones, warm copper,
                    and soft cream colours to create a premium coffee-house identity.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The layout also supports responsive design, accessibility basics, and pure JavaScript interactivity
                    without using external CSS or JavaScript frameworks.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- This values section provides simple content blocks that make the about page look complete and easy to understand. -->
        <section class="values-section section-padding" aria-labelledby="values-title">
            <div class="section-top centered">
                <p class="eyebrow dark">What We Value</p>
                <h2 id="values-title">Our Coffee Principles</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="value-grid">
                <article class="value-card">
                    <h3>Quality Beans</h3>
                    <p>We present the brand as a coffee shop that selects beans carefully for aroma, taste, and balance.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="value-card">
                    <h3>Warm Service</h3>
                    <p>The website tone is friendly and welcoming so customers feel comfortable exploring the brand.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="value-card">
                    <h3>Modern Experience</h3>
                    <p>The site uses interactive features such as theme switching, registration, catalogue search, and reviews.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- This footer gives the website a finished commercial look and provides quick links, customer care links, and contact details similar to a premium coffee brand footer. -->
    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="footer-wrap">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <h2>Alyriss Coffee</h2>
                <p>Premium coffee, calm spaces, better mornings.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-columns">
                <section>
                    <h3>Quick Links</h3>
                    <a href="index.html">Home</a>
                    <a href="catalogue.html">Menu</a>
                    <a href="about.html">About Us</a>
                    <a href="team.html">Our Team</a>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h3>Customer Care</h3>
                    <a href="reviews.html">Customer Reviews</a>
                    <a href="register.html">Member Registration</a>
                    <a href="login.html">Member Login</a>
                    <a href="#">Terms & Conditions</a>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>+60 12-345 6789</p>
                    <p>hello@alyrisscoffee.com</p>
                    <p>City Walk, Kuala Lumpur</p>
                </section>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>Privacy Policy | Terms of Use | Cookies Policy</p>
                <p>© 2026 Alyriss Coffee. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

